WEBVTT

00:03:30.184 --> 00:03:33.513
Katika mapishi unahitaji viungo vizuri

00:03:33.537 --> 00:03:35.150
kupika chakula kizuri.

00:03:35.793 --> 00:03:40.356
Na uongo mzuri unahitaji 
viungo viwili vikuu.

00:03:41.109 --> 00:03:45.219
Kiungo kikuu cha kwanza
ni nadharia ya akili,

00:03:45.243 --> 00:03:47.078
au uwezo wa kusoma- akili.

00:03:47.768 --> 00:03:49.846
Kusoma akili ni uwezo wa kujua

00:03:49.870 --> 00:03:54.478
kwamba watu tofauti wana
ufahamu tofauti kuhusu hali fulani

00:03:54.502 --> 00:03:58.303
na uwezo wa kutofautisha
kati ya ninachojua

00:03:58.327 --> 00:03:59.550
na kile unachojua

00:03:59.914 --> 00:04:02.161
Kusoma akili ni muhimu kwa kudanganya